This folder contains some files to facilitate the work with the Jamoma UserLib.

jcom.userLibPath.maxpat:        To find the absolute path of the UserLib in MaxMSP.
GenerateHTML.maxpat:            Generates fresh HTML reference pages for all UserLib modules
jamoma-userlib-overview.maxpat: An Overview of the Jamoma UserLib modules.

================================================================================================================
HOW TO ADD YOUR MODULES TO THE JAMOMA USERLIB

If you wish to add your modules to the UserLib, please contact the Jamoma team (http://jamoma.org/forum.html).

To keep the UserLib maintenance low, we ask you to respect a few simple guidelines:
1. Please host your modules in a git repository, e.g. at github.com which is free of charge. 
2. Please provide XML preset file and help patch for each module with the module's name (e.g., jmod.myModule.xml).
3. Spaces within file names are not allowed (e.g., "jmod.my module.maxpat").
4. List all 3rd party externals that your modules require.
5. Please provide a contact address for bug reports and feature requests. 
   You may also request an individual project website under http://redmine.jamoma.org/projects/userlibs

